"{\"uid\": \"rollingstone.com-music-music-lists-best-olympics-music-1235066076\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByIlana Kaplan  While the Olympics have consistently delivered some of the most epic sports moments, they have also had a rich history of unforgettable musical performances.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Through empowering anthems and unrivaled collaborations between some of the best artists in the world, many of the opening and closing ceremony performances have remained highlights of the Summer and Winter Olympics over the years.\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 405, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"From London to Rio to Paris, from Celine Dion to One Direction to Stevie Wonder, here are the best of the best.\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 411, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9987273865857169, \"rank\": 0.0012742350226839217, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 421, \"end\": 424, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.651175053684582e-15, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 428, \"end\": 433, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0075514859705584e-26, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 472, \"end\": 485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevie_Wonder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stevie Wonder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevie_Wonder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevie_Wonder\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One Direction was at the peak of their popularity during their performance at the 2012 London Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"During the closing ceremony, the five band members delivered an energetic rendition of their 2011 hit \\\"What Makes You Beautiful\\\" while showcasing their awkward dance moves on a moving truck.\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 820, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2016, Anitta had the opportunity to perform in her hometown of Rio with singer-songwriter and activist-turned-politician Gilberto Gil and songwriter and musician Caetano Veloso at the Rio Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anitta_(singer)\", \"score\": 0.9527818261441746, \"rank\": 0.03687165895513018, \"text\": \"Anitta\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anitta_(singer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anitta_(singer)\"}, {\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 891, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.651175053684582e-15, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 946, \"end\": 958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilberto_Gil\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.505949182817296e-64, \"text\": \"Gilberto Gil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilberto_Gil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gilberto_Gil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The trio brought a vibrant marching band and threw a samba f\\u00eate at the Maracana Stadium as they teamed up for an electrifying collaboration of \\\"Isso Aqui, O Que \\u00c9?\\\"\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1194, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Hey Jude\\\" is always a crowd-pleaser, but Paul McCartney had the entire crowd singing along to the beloved Beatles classic when he performed during the closing ceremony of the 2012 London Olympics.\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_McCartney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.377795652699262e-38, \"text\": \"Paul McCartney\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_McCartney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paul_McCartney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While it was standard fare for any McCartney's concert, it was pretty epic to see the former Beatle on his home turf.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Beatles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beatle\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Beatles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Beatles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2002, KISS rocked out at the Salt Lake City Winter Olympics.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1522, \"end\": 1526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KIIS-FM\", \"score\": 0.9992296358643546, \"rank\": 0.0007709580539476411, \"text\": \"KISS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KIIS-FM\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/KIIS-FM\"}, {\"begin\": 1545, \"end\": 1559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.923403442486158, \"rank\": 0.08295026203014079, \"text\": \"Salt Lake City\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2002_Winter_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As they performed a blistering rendition of 1975's \\\"Rock and Roll All Nite,\\\" figure skaters danced around them as fireworks lit up the Utah sky.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1712, \"end\": 1716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.9999933270023394, \"rank\": 4.813399384716192e-06, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 2008 Beijing Summer Olympics finale prompted an unlikely collaboration to happen - Leona Lewis and Jimmy Page.\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1826, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Page\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jimmy Page\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Page\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Page\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, the singer-songwriter and legendary guitarist performed the 1969 Led Zeppelin classic, \\\"Whole Lotta Love\\\" atop a faux London-to-Beijing bus that turned into a stage.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 2013, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1925, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Led_Zeppelin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5674821326061938e-59, \"text\": \"Led Zeppelin\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Led_Zeppelin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Led_Zeppelin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alongside Page's heavy riffs, Lewis' towering vocals are the star of the performance.\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2044, \"end\": 2049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\", \"score\": 0.9999729261616942, \"rank\": 2.7074532504230833e-05, \"text\": \"Lewis\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lewis_gun\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2010, k.d.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"lang delivered a stirring rendition of Leonard Cohen's hymnal \\\"Hallelujah\\\" during the opening ceremony of the Vancouver Winter Olympics.\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2110, \"end\": 2119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K.d._lang\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"k.d. lang\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K.d._lang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/K.d._lang\"}, {\"begin\": 2154, \"end\": 2167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonard_Cohen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.616294094934786e-85, \"text\": \"Leonard Cohen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonard_Cohen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonard_Cohen\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vancouver Winter Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2010_Winter_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As lang's hypnotic vocals echoed, the entire crowd seemed to sway with lighters in their hands.\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Joined by David Foster on piano and the Atlanta Symphony Orchestra, C\\u00e9line Dion performed the sweeping ballad \\\"The Power of the Dream\\\" at the opening ceremony of the 1996 Atlanta Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2544, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2359, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Foster\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6954909382632134e-74, \"text\": \"David Foster\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Foster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Foster\"}, {\"begin\": 2389, \"end\": 2415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta_Symphony_Orchestra\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Atlanta Symphony Orchestra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta_Symphony_Orchestra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta_Symphony_Orchestra\"}, {\"begin\": 2417, \"end\": 2428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"C\\u00e9line Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Dion's stunning soprano lilt, the David Foster, Linda Thompson and Babyface-penned song served as a true empowerment anthem ahead of the games.\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2584, \"end\": 2596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Foster\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6954909382632134e-74, \"text\": \"David Foster\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Foster\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/David_Foster\"}, {\"begin\": 2598, \"end\": 2612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_D._Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999727152, \"rank\": 2.5311837815508323e-11, \"text\": \"Linda Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_D._Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Linda_D._Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The French band brought some homegrown indie-pop magic to their performance, which featured several special guests, including fellow French legendsAir, who joined Phoenix to deliver \\\"Playground Love\\\" together.\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2699, \"end\": 2705, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9937678026920735, \"rank\": 0.006260578774013069, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2828, \"end\": 2834, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9937678026920735, \"rank\": 0.006260578774013069, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2858, \"end\": 2865, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9228706482048624, \"rank\": 0.0825726690273378, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was also an appearance by DJ-producer Kavinsky, who performed \\\"Nightcall\\\" with singer Ang\\u00e8le.\", \"from\": 2905, \"to\": 3004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2949, \"end\": 2957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kavinsky\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kavinsky\"}, {\"begin\": 2997, \"end\": 3003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ang\\u00e8le_(singer)\", \"score\": 0.9763803861543581, \"rank\": 0.014227642276418916, \"text\": \"Ang\\u00e8le\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ang\\u00e8le_(singer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ang\\u00e8le_(singer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ezra Koenig from Vampire Weekend also joined Phoenix for their collab \\\"Tonight.\\\"\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3086, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3006, \"end\": 3010, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.421518119790173e-12, \"text\": \"Ezra\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ezra_Pound\"}, {\"begin\": 3023, \"end\": 3038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vampire_Weekend\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.2882269594104865e-65, \"text\": \"Vampire Weekend\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vampire_Weekend\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vampire_Weekend\"}, {\"begin\": 3051, \"end\": 3058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9228706482048624, \"rank\": 0.0825726690273378, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phoenix's set concluded with their buoyant hit \\\"1901,\\\" which had the crowd jumping and culminated in a flurry of confetti.\", \"from\": 3087, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3087, \"end\": 3094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9228706482048624, \"rank\": 0.0825726690273378, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just one year prior to releasing her eternal hit \\\"Can not Get You Out of My Head,\\\" Kylie Minogue delivered a charming cover of ABBA's 1976 classic \\\"Dancing Queen\\\" at the 2000 Sydney Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3409, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3294, \"end\": 3307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylie_Minogue\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.49679120601629e-86, \"text\": \"Kylie Minogue\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylie_Minogue\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kylie_Minogue\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clad in a hot pink showgirl costume, the pop icon demonstrated elite showmanship in her home country.\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2012, UK pop singer Jessie J performed with Queen and Freddie Mercury's hologram at the opening ceremony of the London Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 3513, \"to\": 3651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3522, \"end\": 3524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Singles_Chart\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.929792568652509e-15, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Singles_Chart\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Singles_Chart\"}, {\"begin\": 3536, \"end\": 3544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessie_J\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessie J\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessie_J\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessie_J\"}, {\"begin\": 3570, \"end\": 3585, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freddie_Mercury\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Freddie Mercury\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freddie_Mercury\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Freddie_Mercury\"}, {\"begin\": 3628, \"end\": 3650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"London Summer Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Together, they did a raucous version of the sports-stadium standard \\\"We Will Rock You,\\\" with J's throaty belt stealing the show.\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3780, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Spice Girls fans were treated to a pop spectacle when the band reunited at the 2012 London Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 3782, \"to\": 3889, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic Stadium turned into the streets of London as the pop group pulled up in individual taxis before they launched into lovably kitschy medley of \\\"Wannabe\\\" and \\\"Spice Up Your Life.\\\"\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 4078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3937, \"end\": 3943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9987273865857169, \"rank\": 0.0012742350226839217, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the first heavy metal band to play the Olympics, Gojira brought a spectacle to the opening ceremony with a headless Marie Antoinette and explosive pyro.\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4132, \"end\": 4138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.892098980924476e-35, \"text\": \"Gojira\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godzilla\"}, {\"begin\": 4199, \"end\": 4215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2782064553827176e-39, \"text\": \"Marie Antoinette\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marie_Antoinette\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Performing from the windows of the Court of Cassation, the French group delivered a blistering performance of \\\"Ah, \\u00c7a Ira!,\\\" which was popular during the French Revolution, with the opera singer Marina Viotti.\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4295, \"end\": 4301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9937678026920735, \"rank\": 0.006260578774013069, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4438, \"end\": 4444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Battista_Viotti\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.5488367894382726e-12, \"text\": \"Viotti\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Battista_Viotti\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giovanni_Battista_Viotti\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was perhaps the wildest performance the Seine had ever seen.\", \"from\": 4446, \"to\": 4509, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4489, \"end\": 4494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2141736013589648e-14, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the closing ceremony of the 1996 Summer Olympics in Atlanta, Stevie Wonder delivered a tearful rendition of \\\"Imagine\\\" in honor of his late friend John Lennon.\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4570, \"end\": 4577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.376438673014672e-20, \"text\": \"Atlanta\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Atlanta\"}, {\"begin\": 4579, \"end\": 4592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevie_Wonder\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stevie Wonder\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevie_Wonder\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stevie_Wonder\"}, {\"begin\": 4664, \"end\": 4675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lennon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4653169331410489e-22, \"text\": \"John Lennon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\